doctype html
html(lang='en-GB')
  head
    title FLO Blockchain: Teton County Records

    link(rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
    link(rel="icon" href="favicon-v2.png")
    meta(property="og:title" content="FLO Blockchain: Teton County Records")
    meta(property="og:site_name" content="FLO Blockchain")
    meta(property="og:url" content="https://landrecords.mediciland.com")
    meta(
        property="og:description"
        content="Explore the most recent Teton County records in the FLO Blockchain using this floData explorer."
    )
    meta(property="og:type" content="website")
    meta(property="og:image" content="https://floblockchain.org/FLO.png")

  body
    div(id="top" class="floblockchain-header")
      h1
        a(href="https://floblockchain.org") FLO Blockchain
    div(style="text-align:center;")
      img(src="FLO.png" alt="FLO")
      div(class="floblockchain-text top")
        h3 Recent Teton County Records
        a(id="top-link" href="#whats-this") Learn More

    table(id="tbl")
      thead
        tr
          td floData
          td time
          td txid
          td block

      - var classcount=0;
      each tx in data
        tr(class=(1+classcount++)%2 ? 'bg' : '')
          td(class="floData")= tx.tx.floData
          td
            span(title=tx.tx.time)= tx.tx.timeago
          td
            a(href=("http://network.flo.cash/tx/" + tx.tx.txid) target="_blank") #{tx.tx.txid.substring(0, 6) + "..."}
          td
            a(href=("http://network.flo.cash/block/" + tx.tx.blockhash) target="_blank") #{tx.tx.blockhash.substring(0, 6) + "..."}
    div(class="floblockchain-text")
      h2(id="whats-this") About
      p These are the recent Teton Countys recorded in the FLO blockchain. Click on the txid or block hash to navigate to the explorer for further research and verification of individual records.
      h3 Teton County
      p The Medici Land Governance Teton County Blockchain Pilot records warranty deeds, mortgages, releases, liens and so on from 1996 to the present.
      p Learn more about the Teton County system here: [#[a(href="https://youtu.be/S9Zf12bhvwA") YouTube]]
      h3 How was it made?
      p This page was created using #[a(href="https://github.com/oipwg/js-oip") js-oip], a nodejs library that allows you to interact with the Open Index Protocol and the FLO blockchain. The js-oip package is also available on #[a(href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/js-oip") npm].
      p [#[a(href="#top") Back to top]]
